summary: An ordinance authorizing and directing the City Engineer to incur an indebtedness in an amount not to exceed $580.95 against the general fund on account of the cost and expense of the construction of a concrete bulkhead in front of lots 2, 3, 4 and 5, block 1, and lots 1 and 2, block 2, Replat of Green Lake Home Addition, as authorized by Ordinance No. 22819. as provided for in Ordinance No. , creating Local Improvement District No.
